Nested Attribute Example
------------------------

Example project to illustrate the nested_attributes_for feature of Rails 2.3

Based on a presentation by Wolfram Arnold given to the East Bay Ruby Meetup on 7/21/2009 in Berkeley, CA.

Presentation slides: http://www.slideshare.net/wolframarnold/2009-07-21-nested-attributes

